<plot>Chef Chu gets applause everytime he serves his world famous Kung Pao Chicken. But one day something goes terribly wrong. Westerners Chris and Jessica have never learned to eat with a chopstick. Kindly Chris ask for cutlery and Mrs. Chu brings it with abomination. The first time image of the fork tearing the delicious Kung Pao Chicken apart, will stick with Chef Chu forever. It gives him insomnia, it brings him out of his concentration, he is getting nightmares. Something needs to be done to prevent another catastrophe of this proportions.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?299066</url></doc>
